snippet.title: Idioctopus - Out Now!
snippet.description:
Download it now! http://www.idioctopus.com

Idioctopus, Love Don’t Come Easy!
Download Idioctopus and guide brainless lovestruck octopus couples safely to their romantic rendezvous in increasingly deadly date spots.

80 Levels Of Deviously Slimy Puzzles.
Magical teleports, juicy switches, sticky gates, dastardly timers and more keep the gameplay fresh and exciting through 80 brain straining levels. Idioctopus, download it now on PC, Mac, Linux, iOS and Android!
